{"id": 2903, "genre": 1001, "title": "人在职场，你都是如何巧妙解决各种「吃饭难题」的？", "description": "来，让我们自制一本关于如何在办公室科学用餐的职场圣经。（图片来源：istock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 1468, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201904161657083hDVUXKB7i8SLgW9.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-18T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 340224, "content": "平静吃饭，好好休息，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641218}, {"id": 340482, "content": "外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425460}, {"id": 340232, "content": "尽快跟几个相似的人熟悉起来~因为在一个吃饭的群体里，如果有几个人是你比较熟悉的话，吃饭就不会很尬~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664561}, {"id": 340488, "content": "不讲话 一直吃 装傻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378753}, {"id": 340233, "content": "对着大众点评念泥锅泥碗泥混蛋", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641574}, {"id": 340235, "content": "点菜难，不会点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455447}, {"id": 340243, "content": "不知道，怎么给自己年龄差不大小的领导吃饭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641627}, {"id": 340246, "content": "自己做\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638231}, {"id": 340247, "content": "宁可打包回家，也不独自在餐馆用餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633518}, {"id": 340251, "content": "自己带饭。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1626220}, {"id": 340254, "content": "跟同事吃饭，关系一般就瞎侃，最后汇成一句，别听我吹牛逼啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417475}, {"id": 340261, "content": "有钱就吃饭，没钱啃馒头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641678}, {"id": 340262, "content": "便当人士", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834303}, {"id": 339506, "content": "为了掩盖咀嚼的声音，选择掩耳盗铃式用餐：戴耳机听歌吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 339509, "content": "在同事邀约喝奶茶时如何劝解自己并花式say no：最近胖／穷／来姨妈了", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 340277, "content": "最近朋友家里各种蹭\n一个人不想做不想买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641677}, {"id": 339523, "content": "社恐该如何规避跟同事一起点餐尬聊，比如选择每天自己带饭or订健身餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 339525, "content": "办公室用餐气味管理难题，比如：想吃泡面选择去天台吃／躲在会议室开空气净化器吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 340298, "content": "同事问：今天吃啥？\r\n我：吃空气，喝露水....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 340308, "content": "作为大学生的我会到食堂做帮工", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641832}, {"id": 340321, "content": "自己边吃边看手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567055}, {"id": 340067, "content": "每次吃东西时，都说自己正在减肥中。感觉关系并不是很好。所以要感谢一下吃饭更能促进同事关系!", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1638322}, {"id": 340324, "content": "小便池太高……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641904}, {"id": 340070, "content": "多吃菜，少说话，静静听，傻傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 582, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 391490}, {"id": 340072, "content": "不吃午餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352500}, {"id": 340329, "content": "能吃辣吗 \n话题无限延展\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1592953}, {"id": 340074, "content": "本人还是学生", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631494}, {"id": 340075, "content": "难么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 340076, "content": "最好的难道不是一个人在pantry或者店里，边看剧边吃吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635421}, {"id": 340077, "content": "被南方同事们调教得非常能吃辣，作为回报他们也隔三差五被拉着吃顿面食", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624427}, {"id": 340081, "content": "把CPU风扇拆下来，铺一层锡纸煎蛋，再撒点葱花", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573201}, {"id": 340082, "content": "没有难题，想吃就吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555854}, {"id": 340594, "content": "随意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643619}, {"id": 340341, "content": "跟着大佬一起去食堂，顺便聊点工作生活的闲事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484562}, {"id": 340086, "content": "喝酒的(商务)吃肉说话，不喝酒的吃菜保持微笑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696088}, {"id": 340089, "content": "自己带饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1230250}, {"id": 340090, "content": "各吃各的，没有难题", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526235}, {"id": 340091, "content": "中午的话就早点去吃,晚上的话就减肥不吃.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434649}, {"id": 340092, "content": "锻炼谈话技巧才是正道", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276287}, {"id": 340093, "content": "感觉还好，因为离我们最近的菜馆都是十分钟开外，中午只休息一小时。不存在什么难题，只能在公司食堂吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128392}, {"id": 340094, "content": "吃饭？吃什么饭！吃饭是没有前途的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404895}, {"id": 340096, "content": "把在座的各位统统灌趴下（山东人）", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640995}, {"id": 340099, "content": "大家一起吃饭，开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641004}, {"id": 340100, "content": "员工食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534732}, {"id": 340101, "content": "用餐？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 340103, "content": "一个人出去吃，一个人订外卖，很easy", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1398293}, {"id": 340108, "content": "同事问吃啥，回答，随便吃吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641038}, {"id": 340111, "content": "食堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1611049}, {"id": 340115, "content": "要有原则", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1641048}, {"id": 340126, "content": "尽量不吃味道大的东西吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639674}]}